data.description: This 2 story traditional home in a nice Southwest Hastings Neighborhood comes with recent updates you will appreciate, including a newly updated bathroom, furnace, central air and water heater and a newer roof on the garage.  Other features you will appreciate include hardwood floors, fresh paint and newer applances.  The dining area has sliders to a nice deck.  The basement has a roomy family room, laundry and storage.  A fenced back yard and a 2 stall garage complete the package.  Schedule your private showing today!
